{"tid":328891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】馮敬恩圍堵校委會涉刑恐李國章罪名不成立","createTime":"2017-07-20T02:51:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T23:53:45.000Z","uid":5812,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"371e3176c28156cb21e3aed9c4a0103a07b4e003","tid":328891,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T02:51:49.000Z","msg":"港大校務委員會去年1月召開會議，李國章首次以主席身分出席，會後大批學生包圍沙宣道的會議大樓抗議。港大學生會前會長馮敬恩涉高呼「隊冧佢！」恐嚇李國章，被控刑事恐嚇；外務副會長李峯琦亦被控阻礙公職人員執行職務。二人不認罪，案件經審訊今（20日）在西九龍法院裁決。多名社運人士梁頌恆、游蕙禎，另黃台仰、林淳軒及「四眼哥哥」鄭錦滿等到庭支持。"},{"pid":"ca7f6ae825831cc2b5b08856e02766dad08e2a31","tid":328891,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T02:52:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e380e07d307183ad251871f0107b6330eb22599","tid":328891,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T02:52:39.000Z","msg":"【學苑即時】10 ： 48 圍堵沙宣道案中，馮敬恩同學之「刑事恐嚇」罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"528c4b23f5cdfd99994aa98661f6e3d509c1c75e","tid":328891,"uid":104247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T02:53:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff164807344949061b19bc21818ff13fe89b3ec1","tid":328891,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T02:53:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c05cf8135bb350126bce54200412fe721ee668","tid":328891,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T02:54:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 